snippet.title: Windswept - Showcase Trailer
snippet.description:
Marbles 🦆 and Checkers 🐢 were swept away by a storm and they need your help finding their way home!

In this 90s platforming adventure there's a ton of stuff to do and even more to collect.

Coming to home consoles & PC!
Wishlist & play our old (but fun, promise!) 2023 demo on Steam!
https://bit.ly/Windswept-Steam

Press Kit + other social links!
https://bit.ly/Windswept-Carrd

Gamer + Speedrunner Discord!
https://bit.ly/Windswept-D
